{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回\"牡丹楼风波\"叙述萧十一郎与冰冰追查沈璧君行踪。两人先到牡丹楼向吕掌柜打听蒙面姑娘来历，得知她们每夜来却不吃不喝，账由年轻后生付。到连云栈找牛掌柜得知姑娘住东跨院。萧十一郎在牡丹楼遇花如玉，花如玉称沈璧君已离开去找连城璧。萧十一郎愤怒与花如玉拼酒，花如玉假装醉倒。等萧十一郎离开后，花如玉与同伙心心对话，揭露绑架沈璧君和风四娘，准备将风四娘卖给老色鬼。萧十一郎与冰冰漫步时发现花如玉马车疾驰，返回连云栈人去楼空，在床底发现风四娘乌木簪。最后牛掌柜透露姑娘已搬到对面跨院。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "吕掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那两位蒙着黑纱的姑娘，这三天的确每夜都来，叫了\n\n一桌子菜，却又不吃不喝，每天都要等到打烊时才走，可是她们给的小账很多，所以每个伙计都很欢迎她们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "账是谁付的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "吕掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是跟她们来的那位年轻后生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "吕掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说他们在连云栈包下了个大跨院，而且先付了十天的房钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "牛掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那两位脸上蒙着黑纱的姑娘，可真是奇怪，白天她们连房门都不出，连饭都是送到屋里去吃的，一到天快黑的时候，就上牡丹楼，来了这三天，这里还没有人听她们说过一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她们住在哪间屋子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "牛掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在东跨院，整个院子她们都包了下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "牛掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚回来！\"他搔着头，又道：\"她们既然是从牡丹楼回来的，本该已吃得很饱才对，可是她们回来了，偏偏又叫了一整桌酒菜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那桌菜也许是叫给我们来吃的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "牛掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她们知道两位会来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位既然已来了，为什么不进来喝杯酒？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人请我喝酒，我是从来不会拒绝的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来就在恭候两位的大驾。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈姑娘她们跟着公子，难道公子从来也不让她们坐下来吃饭的？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有替她们准备位子，只因为她们已不在这里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就让她们走了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下既不是土匪，也不是官差，她们要走，在下怎么留得住她们？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧大侠莫非不相信我的话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看来的确不像土匪，只不过人不可貌相，这句话你想必也知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下有什么理由要对萧大侠说谎？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你不愿让我看到她们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下若不愿让萧大侠见着她们，为什么要回到这里来？\n\n为什么要在这里恭候萧大侠的大驾？\"\n\n萧十一郎说不出话了。\n\n花如玉叹了口气，道：　\"在下在此相候，为的就是要向萧大侠解释刚才的误会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才有什么误会？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下与沈姑娘相识，只不过三五天而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈姑娘本来一直都在跟着樱、柳两位老前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红樱绿柳？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧大侠若是不信，随时都可以去问他们，这两位前辈总是不会说谎的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她怎么又跟你到这里来了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是在下不肯说，只不过……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过在下唯恐萧大侠听了，会不高兴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若不说，我才会生气，我生气的时候，总是很不讲理的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖传闻，都说连城璧连公子已到了这地方，沈姑娘听见了这消息，就一定要随在下到这里来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她的人虽已不在，酒却还在，萧大侠不如先开怀畅饮几杯，遣此长夜。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！我敬你三杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恭敬不如从命，请。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这酒杯不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这酒杯太小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我喝。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次该你敬我了，主人当然也得先喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我敬了你，你难道不敬我？你看不起我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我就回敬萧大侠三碗。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来，我们再来三碗，萧大侠请。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还有两件事要告诉你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一，我既不是大侠，也从来不做大侠。\n\n第二，我若发现你对我说了一个字谎话，我就把你这根大舌头割下来，你明白了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白了，可是我还有点不明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事不明白？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她既然是为连城璧来的，现在想必也是为了连城璧走的，你为什么不去找他们，反而找我来出气？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然有心要请我，吃不完的我就带走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在恶客已走了，你还不醒？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人好厉害，居然真要灌醉我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你的酒量远比他想像中要好得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这个人却比他想像中要坏得多。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中若再要选十大恶人，你一定是其中之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然也跑不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈璧君是不是已走了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已叫白老三带着她走了，也已将你的吩咐告诉了白老三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个女疯子呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怕男疯子到后面去找她，所以只好先请她到床底下去休息休息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你已可请她出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后再请她干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后再请她洗个澡，好好的替她打扮打扮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也听说一个人要进棺材的时候，总是要先打扮打扮的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还不想她进棺材。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为她还很值钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道想卖了她？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据我所知，有个老色鬼想她已想了很多年。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么样的老色鬼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是个有钱的老色鬼，而且也舍得花钱的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真是个大恶人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ru_yu",
      "speaker_name": "花如玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来就是的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在打什么算盘，萧十一郎只怕连做梦都想不到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过想提醒你，这里面有炖鸡、烧肉、水晶肘子、糖醋鱼，还有一整只八宝鸭子，你若是饿了，随便想吃什么，这里面都有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我刚才应该弄他一坛酒出来的，在这里喝酒真不错。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实无论在什么地方，只要有酒喝都不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个人说的话，你真相信？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我连一个字都不信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然不信，为什么要走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道要我陪着他躺在地上睡觉？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不到后面去找？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找也找不到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还没有找，怎么知道找不到？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像他那种人，若是不愿让我见到她们，我怎么找得到？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看得出他是个很狡猾的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我第一眼看到他时，就想到了一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小公子，那个比毒蛇还毒一百倍的小公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个人当然不是小公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是个男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个男人长得虽然娘娘腔，却是个货真价实的男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能确定？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论他是女扮男装也好，是男扮女装也好，我有个法子，一试就能试出他究竟是男是女来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这个法子也是独门秘方，次次见效，从来也没有失灵过一次。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摸他一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我刚才已乘你不注意的时候，摸了他一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你一定也醉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我醉了，我现在简直清醒得像猫头鹰一样。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不醉的时候，没有这么坏的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的以为我是个好人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管别人怎么样看你，只有我知道，你是个……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是刚才那个人的马车。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三更半夜的，他们如此急着赶车，是去干什么呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许车上没有人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只要一看车轮后带起的沙尘，就知道车上是不是有人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你的眼睛比大盗萧十一郎还厉害。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至少比一个喝醉了的大盗萧十一郎厉害些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们追上去看看好不好？看那小子究竟在玩什么花样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一定没有看见我们，一定认为我们早已坐车走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才赶车的那个车夫，已经不是原来那个了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "车上虽然有人，但却好像只有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们再回连云栈去看看好不好？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们已全都走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但车上却只有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他们不是一路走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然是一路来的，为什么不一路走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他们知道我们又回来了，都藏到床底下去了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见过这个乌木簪？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在什么地方看见过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在一个人的头发上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在谁的头发上？沈姑娘？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你永远猜不出这个人是谁的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非是风四娘？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜出来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个连走路都要人扶的妇人，莫非就是风四娘？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定就是她，她刚才一定还在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 537,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管怎么样，我们只要找到那小子，总能问得出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_bing",
      "speaker_name": "冰冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们只要找到那辆马车，就能找到那个人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们现在就去找。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们都是很节俭的人，吃不完的菜，我们总是带着走的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 573
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "牛掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位是不是要把地上这些菜再包起来，送到对面去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是个好人，我喜欢你，这些菜我都送给你带回去宵夜了，你千万别客气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "牛掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些菜都送给你带回去宵夜，你千万别客气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 599
    }
